A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Criminal Law – Misdemeanor Theft – Statute of Limitations
3 FOR the purpose of altering the statute of limitations applicable to the crime of theft of
4 property or services with a certain value; and generally relating to theft.
